This project was created to explore how **machine learning can assist medical risk prediction**.

The emphasis is on:

* Responsible model evaluation
* Handling imbalanced medical datasets
* Interpretable AI for healthcare decision support

Understanding *why* a model predicts stroke risk is just as important as the prediction itself.
